proposal:
Dear Tilden Hotel,

Recognizing the Tilden Hotel's reputation as a premier San Francisco destination, especially with its art-focused atmosphere and prime location, we propose a new professional website to drive more direct bookings. A modern, user-friendly website will showcase your unique amenities, including the rooftop terrace and art installations, making it easier for guests to discover and book their stay. By highlighting positive customer reviews and offering seamless online booking, you can increase revenue and build even stronger relationships with your guests.

We are confident that our services will significantly elevate the Tilden Hotel's online presence and contribute to your continued success. We would welcome the opportunity to discuss how we can create a website that reflects your distinctive brand. Please contact us to schedule a consultation.
